title: Glacier Landscape
description: A stunning view of a glacier descending from a rocky mountain into a serene lake. The glacier is a vibrant blue, contrasting with the gray rocks and green vegetation surrounding it. The scene captures the beauty of nature, showcasing the rugged terrain and the calm water reflecting the landscape.

title: Polluted Waterway
description: A river or stream with a winding shape, displaying a mix of blue and gray hues, likely indicating pollution. The banks are lined with patches of yellow and green grass, contrasting with the unnatural colors of the water.

title: Underground Cave with Water
description: A serene underground cave featuring clear water reflecting the rocky surroundings. The cave walls are rugged and uneven, with various sizes of rocks scattered throughout the water. Soft lighting highlights the textures of the rocks and the tranquil surface of the water.

title: Polluted Water Discharge
description: The image shows two pipes discharging dark, murky wastewater into a river. The surrounding area appears to be muddy, indicating possible erosion or contamination. The water in the river is also discolored, suggesting pollution.

title: Drainage Outlet
description: The image shows a drainage outlet where water is flowing out of a large pipe into a body of water. The water appears murky and turbulent, with waves crashing at the outlet. The surrounding area is grassy and there are structures visible in the background.

title: Polluted Water Surface
description: The image depicts a body of water littered with various types of debris, including plastic bottles and a wooden crate. The water appears to be a deep blue, contrasting with the colorful pieces of trash floating on the surface.
